-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DuckieTV{{NIGHTLY}} - The TV Show Tracker You've been waiting for - {{VERSION}}
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INSTALL
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

To install DuckieTV run "sudo ./setup" in terminal.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
UNINSTALL
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

To remove all DuckieTV components run "sudo ./setup --uninstall" in terminal.

